<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">이렇게 입력하고 오른쪽 <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">제출</code></strong> 버튼 클릭</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">그러면 아래 "제출된 사이트맵" 표에 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sitemap.xml</code>이 나타나고 상태가 <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">성공</code></strong> 으로 바뀌면 완료예요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">혹시 제출했는데 <strong>오류</strong>가 뜨면 스크린샷 보내주세요. GitHub에 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sitemap.xml</code> 파일이 제대로 올라갔는지 확인해볼게요!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
