<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">GA4 연동 확인하는 법</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">지금 코드에 이미 GA4 태그가 들어가 있어요. 제대로 작동하는지 확인만 하면 돼요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>1단계 - GA4 실시간 확인</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://analytics.google.com/">analytics.google.com</a> 접속</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">왼쪽 메뉴 <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">보고서</code></strong> → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">실시간</code></strong> 클릭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">내 사이트(<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">luna5813.github.io/cherry-blossom-map/</code>) 직접 열기</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">실시간 화면에 <strong>사용자 1명</strong> 뜨면 연동 성공 ✅</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>2단계 - 이벤트 확인</strong> (명당 제보 버튼 눌렀을 때)</p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">GA 이벤트명</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">언제 발생</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">cherry_click_add_start</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">📍명당 제보 버튼 클릭 시</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">cherry_complete_registration</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">장소 등록 완료 시</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">cherry_vote_interaction</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">👍맞아요 / ⚠️신고 클릭 시</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">GA4 → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">보고서</code></strong> → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">참여도</code></strong> → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">이벤트</code></strong> 에서 확인 가능해요.</p>
