<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">1. images 폴더 + og-image 넣기</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">GitHub 웹에서 폴더는 직접 못 만들고, <strong>파일 올릴 때 경로에 폴더명 쓰면</strong> 자동 생성돼요.</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">cherry-blossom-map</code> repo에서 <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Add file</code></strong> → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Upload files</code></strong> 클릭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">벚꽃 이미지 파일 드래그 (없으면 아래에서 만들어드릴게요)</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">파일 올리기 전에 <strong>경로 입력칸</strong>에</li>
</ol>
<div role="group" aria-label="코드" tabindex="0" class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-100"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 group-focus-within/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
