<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">2. Google Search Console 인증 파일 넣기</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">한강 repo에 있는 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">google96...html</code> 파일이 Search Console 소유권 인증 파일이에요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">벚꽃은 이미 Search Console 등록했으니까 <strong>인증 파일 다운받아서 올려야 해요.</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://search.google.com/search-console">search.google.com/search-console</a> 접속</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">벚꽃 속성 선택</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">왼쪽 <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">설정</code></strong> → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">소유권 확인</code></strong> 클릭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">HTML 파일</code></strong> 탭 클릭</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">google******.html</code> 파일 다운로드</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">GitHub <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">cherry-blossom-map</code> repo → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Add file</code></strong> → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Upload files</code></strong> 로 올리기</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">og-image 없으면 제가 만들어드릴까요?</h2>
