          ease-[cubic-bezier(0.165,0.85,0.45,1)] h-8 w-8 rounded-md _fill_1abo4_9 _ghost_1abo4_96" type="button" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-300"><path d="M69.12,94.15,28.5,128l40.62,33.85a8,8,0,1,1-10.24,12.29l-48-40a8,8,0,0,1,0-12.29l48-40a8,8,0,0,1,10.24,12.3Zm176,27.7-48-40a8,8,0,1,0-10.24,12.3L227.5,128l-40.62,33.85a8,8,0,1,0,10.24,12.29l48-40a8,8,0,0,0,0-12.29ZM162.73,32.48a8,8,0,0,0-10.25,4.79l-64,176a8,8,0,0,0,4.79,10.26A8.14,8.14,0,0,0,96,224a8,8,0,0,0,7.52-5.27l64-176A8,8,0,0,0,162.73,32.48Z"></path></svg></button></div></div><div id="mcp-app-placeholder-toolu_011TPosnk2DZuJefN5o8TYZX" class="w-full" style="height: 0px;"></div><div id="mcp-app-container-toolu_011TPosnk2DZuJefN5o8TYZX" class="w-full" style=""><div class="h-full w-full"><iframe sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-forms" allow="fullscreen *; clipboard-write *" src="./og-image_files/mcp_apps.html" style="width: 100%; border: none; background-color: transparent; height: 504px;"></iframe></div></div></div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">OG 이미지 완성이에요! 1200×630px 규격이에요.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">이제 저장해서 올려야 하는데, SVG는 GitHub Pages에서 OG 이미지로 안 읽혀요. <strong>PNG로 변환해서 올려야 해요.</strong></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">저장 방법</h2>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>방법 1 - 간단하게</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">위 이미지에서 우클릭 → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">이미지를 다른 이름으로 저장</code></strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">파일명: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">og-image.png</code>으로 저장</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>방법 2 - 더 선명하게</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://svgtopng.com/">svgtopng.com</a> 접속</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">SVG 코드 붙여넣기 → PNG 다운로드</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h2 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">GitHub에 올리는 법</h2>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">cherry-blossom-map</code> repo → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Add file</code></strong> → <strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Upload files</code></strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">파일 업로드 창에 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">og-image.png</code> 드래그</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">커밋 전에 파일 경로를 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">images/og-image.png</code> 로 바꿔야 해요
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">업로드 후 파일명 앞에 <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">images/</code> 붙이는 칸이 있어요</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Commit changes</code></strong> 클릭</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">이미지 색상이나 텍스트 수정 원하시면 말씀해주세요!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
  items-center
  justify-center
  relative
  isolate
  shrink-0
  can-focus
  select-none
  disabled:pointer-events-none
  disabled:opacity-50
